description.en:
TotoroInu is a utility token which will be used on the upcoming launchpad, TotoroPad, a multi-chain, anime themed launchpad with a refund system to ensure your security and satisfaction. As a coin that stealth launched on 28/10/21 with a starting market cap of $4000 and reaching $5.3 million in 12 days, we have a strong community behind us. 
TotoroInu has a 11% tax which is split into 4% LP 7% Marketing and Development. This is a community-powered coin, with most of our moves & progress is being made from the decisions the community makes as a whole.
